name: Jeans Dress
description:
Get early access to build and test build, be able to try all epochs and test them by yourself on Patreon or contact me for support on Discord

To support me you can buy me a coffe at https://ko-fi.com/antonioriolo

Recommended settings:

  • Make sure you are aware on the usage instructions of LORA

  • Sampler: DPM++ SDE Karras (Recommended for best quality, you may try other samplers)

  • CFG Scale : 5 to 10

  • LORA weight for txt2img: reccomended 0.4-0.7.

  • Keys: wearing jeans dress, wearing jeans salopette

Very easy to use, just use the keyword with the proper weight.

This is wierd model, i have to say it, i trained it with jeans salopettes trying to teach this clothing, but it ended up drawing all kind of jeans dresses, elegant ones, short ones, he has no idea what a jeans salopette is, it just come up from times to times.

The original keywords were "wearing jeans salopette, jeans dress" but somehow if i insert in the prompt "wearing jeans salopette" with most prompts he doesn't draw a jeans salopette, no idea why.

So i renamed it as jeans_dress and pubblished it this way, you may find a few images with salopette_clothing lora name, that's jeans_dress model, i just didn't rename it at that point, i did it only after creating these images and understing he had no idea of salopettes.

All the images with many women are created using controlnet, if you want to replicate them, download my poses packs for 2 and 3 women, you can find them in my models page and follow the instructions on how to use them and how to install controlnet on SD.

Enjoy!

If you'd like to support my efforts and have access to early and bleeding edge builds, please think about joining my Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/betterCuteAsians
